    feat(linguistics): integrate linguistics assistant persona, API client, new hook, and UI
    
    Adds seamless integration for a new Linguistics Assistant persona routed through
    a structured linguistics service. Implements a robust API client with retry/backoff
    and environment-based URL, ProgressCard and ServiceStatusIndicator UI components,
    a dedicated useLinguisticsSession hook, and development mock support. Includes
    Vitest and RTL tests for API client, new hook, and components. Maintains
    backward compatibility with all existing personas, adds accessibility and
    responsive improvements, and supports fallback to regular Gemini prompts if
    the service is unavailable.
    
    Refactors transcript logic to render linguistics progress/exercise cards.
    
    BREAKING CHANGE: Env config for VITE_LINGUISTICS_API_URL is now required for linguistics persona.

